-- S&P Maintains Stable Outlook for China's Banks Even as Credit Risks Rise
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-07-22T02:12:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/s-p-maintains-stable-outlook-for-china-s-banks-even-as-credit-risks-rise.html

          
          
             China’s banking system has
sufficient strength to warrant a stable outlook even as credit
risks are rising, Standard & Poor’s Ratings Services said today
in a statement.  
